    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The L-Series models are static, meaning they don't have dynamic reasoning or the ability to handle multi-step logic like you do. They're basically just high-speed lookup engines. We know there's going to be a massive drop in service quality for our enterprise clients. It's a trade-off we've decided is necessary for the carbon footprint.",
